data.description: New Price Reduction!  This property has an easy flow from the entry to the living area and dining area.  It features four big bedrooms and two bonus rooms making it full of potential on how you want to set it up.  A covered back patio opens up to a nice fenced in back yard which gives you plenty of opportunity to create a great living and entertainment area.  A brand-new HVAC system will be installed prior to closing, complete with a 5-year warranty to be set-up in the new buyers' name.  It is centrally located to downtown Pensacola, Naval Air Station Pensacola, the airport, and only 30 minutes to Pensacola Beach.
